{"word":"καταψεύδομαι","slug":"καταψεύδομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταψεύδομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> <el>-ψεύσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-έψευσμαι</el>,) (aor1 <el>-εψεύσθην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, <i>to tell lies against, speak falsely of</i>, <el>τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to allege falsely against</i>, <el>τί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to say falsely, pretend</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <i>to feign, invent</i>, <el>τι</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>also as <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be falsely reported</i>: of writings, <i>to be spurious</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}